         <div type="translation" source="#irt2009" xml:lang="en">
            <p>One who lived honourably and respected for his way of life, honoured ?with official honours, being of singulars skill and wholly informed in many tasks, Lucius, here the black earth of Libya conceals you. Sostratos <supplied reason="subaudible">set this up</supplied> for Lucius, his own nursling , who lived for twenty-one years; in memory.</p><p> Hail, passers-by!</p></div>
